name: DECEPTION / DEMONIC SLAUGHTER - WORSHIPPERS OF THE DARKNESS SPLIT DIGIPACK
description: DECEPTION’s side features 3 brand new tracks saturated with a sinister old school Death Metal, while DEMONIC SLAUGHTER’s stuff combines raw Black Metal with some Death Metal elements and a guest appearance of Gonthy from SOUL SNATCHER, MOON and ABUSIVENESS. Exlusive tracks only to be released on this exceptional mini album

name: Hetzer " Fall Of The Holy Cult" CD
description: "Fall of The Holy Cult" is the newest over thisty-minutes , uholy offensive kept in the old school black death metal style. Tremendous blasts, sawing riffs and demented vocals, armed with pitch black sound altogether may give you a taste of the newest Hetzer work. Hetzer Kills , The Kult is Falls!!!

name: Stillborn "Esta Rebelión Es Eterna" CD
description: Stillborn strikes back with an unique tribute album „Esta Rebelión Es Eterna". This flaming homage to blasphemous metal consists of five individual songs, and four surprising cover songs of bands which created the foundations of genre. The album was produced and mixed in Factory Studio, Debica (PL) by Janusz Bryt. The records and sound works took a few weekends of the first half of current twelvemonth. The guest appearance was again performed by Destroyer (Kriegsmaschine, Hate). The layout and whole graphic phlegm was breed by ataman Tolovy.
